data.description: Charming 3 bed, 2 bath ranch-style home in prime locale. Kitchen boasts stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and an inviting open layout. Enjoy the convenience of a cozy, yet spacious living area perfect for gatherings. Relax in the comfort of three well-appointed bedrooms. Ideally situated for easy access to amenities and transportation. Don’t miss this opportunity to make this delightful home yours!    NOTE: Principals of the seller may share ownership in a licensed real estate brokerage.
